  ---
  Architecture

  Event-Driven Analytics Flow:
  User Activity (TaskCompleted, HabitCompleted, etc.)
      ↓
  Event Bus Routes Event
      ↓
  CrossDomainAnalyticsService Updates Neo4j
      ↓
  Analytics Nodes Updated in Real-Time
      ↓
  GET /api/analytics/* Queries for Live Metrics

  Report Generation Flow:
  Milestone Event (GoalAchieved, HabitStreakMilestone, etc.)
      ↓
  Event Bus Routes to ReportService
      ↓
  ReportService.handle_*_event()
      ↓
  generate_report() creates markdown file
      ↓
  Saved to /data/reports/{domain}/{date}_{uid}.md

  ---
  Performance Benefits

  Zero Polling Required:
  - Before (Traditional): Poll database every 5 minutes for metric updates → O(n) full table scans
  - After (Event-Driven): Metrics updated immediately when events occur → O(1) event handling

  Real-Time Updates:
  - Task completed → Productivity metrics updated instantly
  - Habit logged → Consistency score recalculated immediately
  - KU mastered → Learning velocity updated in real-time

